OL,3,CYoung people skipping meals to afford
OL,4,Cbus fares in Oxford, report finds
OL,6,FThere are calls for free bus fares for
OL,7,Fstudents across Oxford after a new
OL,8,Freport found some young people are
OL,9,Fhaving to skip meals to afford them.
OL,11,FOxford Citizens, which is made up of
OL,12,Flocal churches, schools, charities and
OL,13,Fcommunity groups, gathered the views
OL,14,Fof more than 7,500 local people.
OL,16,FThey found bus fares can be a barrier
OL,17,Fto accessing school and college.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
