OL,3,CYoung people skipping meals to afford
OL,4,Cbus fares in Oxford, report finds
OL,6,FOxford student Amanda Okpere says to
OL,7,Frevise for her A-levels, she would
OL,8,Fsometimes walk two hours a day between
OL,9,Fher home in Rose Hill and the library
OL,10,Fin Oxford.
OL,12,FFor Amanda, the bus fare was just too
OL,13,Fexpensive.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
