PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783694874
OL,3,CYoung people skipping meals to afford
OL,4,Cbus fares in Oxford, report finds
OL,6,FShe said: "It does take a toll on my
OL,7,Feducation because I'm like 'Oh I can't
OL,8,Fnecessarily go to the library and
OL,9,Fstudy in a quieter place' because I've
OL,10,Fgot quite a lot of siblings, so when I
OL,11,Fwant to go study in the library I
OL,12,Fcan't always do that, which means that
OL,13,Fmy concentration levels are not there.
OL,15,F"I'm not getting as much efficient
OL,16,Fwork as I'd like to and I know that is
OL,17,Fthe same for my friends which is quite
OL,18,Fannoying and it does impact my grades
OL,19,Fand it is noticeable."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
