PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783694874
OL,3,CYoung people skipping meals to afford
OL,4,Cbus fares in Oxford, report finds
OL,6,FAmanda is just one of thousands of
OL,7,Fschool students in the city who need
OL,8,Fto use the bus to access education.
OL,9,FBut for some families on a lower
OL,10,Fincome, they just can't afford it.
OL,12,FDepending on how you pay, a single bus
OL,13,Fjourney for a young person can cost
OL,14,Fanywhere between #1 and #2.30.
OL,16,FDeputy Head of 6th Form at The Oxford
OL,17,FAcademy, Louisa Wilkinson, said: "Some
OL,18,Fof our students sometimes have to take
OL,19,Fup to three buses from one side of
OL,20,FOxford to the other and the cost rises
OL,21,Freally significantly.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
