CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783694874
OL,3,CYoung people skipping meals to afford
OL,4,Cbus fares in Oxford, report finds
OL,6,F"For some of our students it can be as
OL,7,Fmuch as #8 pounds a day to travel from
OL,8,Fhome to school.
OL,10,F"For some students from low income
OL,11,Ffamilies there may be on some days a
OL,12,Fchoice between coming to school and
OL,13,Fnot coming to school because of the
OL,14,Fcost of transport, and that shouldn't
OL,15,Fhappen."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
