OL,3,CYoung people skipping meals to afford
OL,4,Cbus fares in Oxford, report finds
OL,6,FOxford Citizens, a community alliance
OL,7,Fthat campaigns on issues that affect
OL,8,Fresidents, listened to more than 7,500
OL,9,Flocal people and found the price of
OL,10,Ftransport can be a barrier to
OL,11,Feducation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
