PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783694874
OL,3,CYoung people skipping meals to afford
OL,4,Cbus fares in Oxford, report finds
OL,6,FOxford Citizens member, Sybil Romain,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We should be about trying to
OL,8,Fencourage those from low incomes to
OL,9,Fstay in education and the buses,
OL,10,Fhaving to pay such a significant
OL,11,Famount, there's a real temptation to
OL,12,Fgive up after school and go into full
OL,13,Ftime work, which means they'll never
OL,14,Fadvance because they'll be in low paid
OL,15,Fwork, which means that their families
OL,16,Fand they in turn will be affected by
OL,17,Fthis."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
