PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783694874
OL,3,CYoung people skipping meals to afford
OL,4,Cbus fares in Oxford, report finds
OL,6,FOxfordshire County Council declined an
OL,7,Finterview, but they did send us
OL,8,Finformation about a variety of schemes
OL,9,Fwhich can lower the cost of bus fares
OL,10,Ffor students.
OL,12,FBut many of these schemes are for
OL,13,Funder 18s only, which means it's not
OL,14,Fhelpful for older students.
OL,16,FAlso, most require some sort of
OL,17,Fupfront fee, whether that's paying for
OL,18,Fa week or a month in advance, which
OL,19,Fisn't accessible for some lower income
OL,20,Ffamilies.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
