PN,38909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1783694874
OL,3,CYoung people skipping meals to afford
OL,4,Cbus fares in Oxford, report finds
OL,6,FAmanda Okpere added: "What I've
OL,7,Fnoticed in places like London,
OL,8,Fstudents who are 18 years and under
OL,9,Fand in full time education do have
OL,10,Flike discounted prices or free travel.
OL,12,F"I feel like if we could implement
OL,13,Fthat over here in Oxford it would just
OL,14,Fgreatly help students and it would
OL,15,Fmake the difference between them going
OL,16,Fto like the after school activity or
OL,17,Fgetting that job interview or that
OL,18,Fcollege open day."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
